<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="invention-n">invention <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'venʃn/    美 /ɪn'venʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>发明；研制：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Necessity is the mother of invention. 
发明源于需要。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>发明物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Four Great inventions
四大发明</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>捏造；虚构：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The story was a complete invention. 
本故事纯属虚构。</p></div></div>